document_title: Buffer overflow in TFTP client library of CLI

note.text: A buffer overflow [CWE-121] in the TFTP client library of FortiOS, may allow an authenticated local attacker to achieve arbitrary code execution via specially crafted command line arguments.
note.title: Summary

acknowledgment.description: Internally discovered and reported by Giuseppe Cocomazzi of Fortinet Product Security team.
